      "rationale": "A bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model (E = 114 GPa, sigma_y = 880 MPa, E_t = 1.2 GPa for Ti-6Al-4V ELI) was adopted, consistent with published tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrangian frictional contact (mu = 0.2, screw-to-block interface) was verified to reproduce the load-displacement linearity observed in the elastic regime. The model form is judged appropriate for the declared QoIs."
