      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from two production lots and tested across two laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). Dimensional inspection confirmed all specimens within drawing tolerances. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for yield force was 3.8%, indicating acceptable test reproducibility."
