      "rationale": "All testing was performed at a single displacement rate (5 mm/min) under ambient laboratory conditions per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition (compression-bending at 5 mm/min) was evaluated; no variation in displacement rate or temperature was explored. This factor is assessed below the required level, consistent with the COU description noting a single test condition limitation. This known gap is acknowledged in the decision record."
