      "rationale": "The normalised validation metric E/uval was computed for each QoI incorporating simulation numerical uncertainty (GCI-derived), model input uncertainty (Monte Carlo, N=500), and experimental measurement uncertainty (combined standard uncertainty from calibration records and inter-laboratory variability). Results: stiffness E/uval = 0.93, yield force E/uval = 1.41, force at 40 mm E/uval = 1.17. All below 1.96. Mean absolute percentage error 6.3%."
